WEBVTT

00:11.678 --> 00:13.429
My name is Nash Olsen.

00:13.430 --> 00:16.804
I am a PMC... a private
military contractor.

00:17.976 --> 00:20.770
At least, that's what
they call us now.

00:20.771 --> 00:23.272
People used to call us mercenaries,

00:23.273 --> 00:26.567
guns for hire, soldiers of fortune.

00:26.568 --> 00:28.319
Whatever they call us,

00:28.320 --> 00:31.322
the job always stays the same.

00:31.323 --> 00:34.325
When shit really hits the fan

00:34.326 --> 00:37.662
and the military can't touch it,

00:37.663 --> 00:39.456
they give us a call.

00:41.333 --> 00:42.917
The commando team of four,

00:42.918 --> 00:45.253
been together for about eight years

00:45.254 --> 00:48.339
with dozens of missions
all over the world,

00:48.340 --> 00:50.341
never lost a man.

00:50.342 --> 00:52.927
We live and die by our motto...

00:52.928 --> 00:55.721
no one left behind.

00:55.722 --> 00:59.308
These words are really
important to us.

00:59.309 --> 01:02.103
Just like any soldiers,

01:02.104 --> 01:05.147
we know the risk of each mission.

01:05.147 --> 01:08.067
But we also know and
trust each other

01:08.068 --> 01:10.771
with our lives every single day.

01:12.656 --> 01:15.157
That is until the day you wake up

01:15.158 --> 01:17.285
and you realize

01:17.286 --> 01:20.913
that you are in way over your head

01:20.914 --> 01:23.537
and there is no one who can help.

01:25.085 --> 01:27.253
This is our story.

